    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, totally ready for many more adventures! It drives super smoothly and has been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
