    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery through the corners. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including professional reinforcement of the rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis remains sharp with refreshed bushings and a balanced weight distribution. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved performance machine, the mechanical vitals and compression numbers remain strong, making this an ideal specimen for the purist seeking a visceral driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
