    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, showing only the lightest evidence of careful road use, with body panels that are straight and free of significant blemishes. Step inside to find an interior that has been treated with the utmost care; the seats are firm and supportive with only minor natural creasing, and the cabin remains a smoke-free environment. All onboard electronics, from the climate control to the premium sound system, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a consistent maintenance schedule that is evident the moment you pull away from the curb. The transmission shifts are crisp and intuitive, and the suspension provides a composed, comfortable ride. With a set of high-tread tires and a clean bill of health from its last service, this car is ready to provide its next owner with years of dependable service and driving pleasure.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
